Package: postgresql-14-pg-duckdb
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-14
Description: DuckDB embedded in PostgreSQL (PostgreSQL 14)
 pg_duckdb integrates DuckDB's columnar-vectorized analytics engine into
 PostgreSQL, enabling high-performance analytics and data-intensive applications.
 .
 This package provides the pg_duckdb extension for PostgreSQL 14.

